name: iOQ Wallet
description: iOQ is a secure, intelligent, non-custodial web wallet built for the next era of decentralized finance and digital identity. Powered by advanced AI, it delivers seamless multi-chain compatibility, enabling users to manage assets, NFTs, and DeFi activities with ease. With future-ready cryptography, it ensures top-tier security, privacy, and resilience. Designed for both beginners and experts, iOQ combines cutting-edge technology with an intuitive interface, offering features like AI-driven insights, cross-chain transactions, and integrated DeFi tools, empowering users to stay ahead in the fast-evolving Web3 landscape. Many more innovative features are on the way.
